::Battera::

She flies in through a hatch and into the Pred base.

"Battera, Terrorize!"  She TF's into her bot mode.

She looks around the room she is in.
"Gee, so much for the welcome wagon."
She walked untill she came to a room.
"Hmm what have we here?"
She saw tables and reprogramming equipment.  She saw a spare CR chamber.  A 
hole blown threw a wall, and a mess of scrap metal on the floor.

"It looks like a small war was faught in here.  Well, none of my biz 
anyhow."

She continued on looking for something to do.
